==-. ABS Backup System .-==

1. QUICK START

  1. Copy abs to /usr/local/sbin/abs
  2. Edit and copy abs.conf to /usr/local/etc/abs/abs.conf
  3. Edit and copy exclude.conf to /usr/local/etc/abs/exclude.conf
  4. Add host keys to /root/.ssh/known_hosts.
  5. Copy backup system SSH public key to remote hosts.
  6. Edit and copy abs.cron to /etc/cron.d/abs


==-. ARMS Remote Mirror System .-==

1. QUICK START

  1. Copy arms to /usr/local/sbin/arms
  2. Add host keys to /root/.ssh/known_hosts.
  3. Copy backup system SSH public key to remote hosts.
  4. Edit and copy abs.cron to /etc/cron.d/abs

